data.description: Adorable Gated Townhome Community, centrally located near shopping restaurants in close proximity to Shopping and the Las Vegas Strip. This 3 bedroom, 3 bath in excellent condition.  Covered Carport and additional uncovered parking space * Updated Kitchen, Wood Beam Accents, Tile floors, Woodburning Fireplace* Large Enclosed Courtyard* Primary Bedroom with Vaulted Ceilings and Balcony w/bath and walk in closet.   Greenwood offers a large community pool, mature landscaping and tennis courts! Lots of Charm and Character!
